      "content": "# payment-terms model defines payment conditions and schedules\n\n`powerhouse/payment-terms` (16 ops) configures the conditions under which payments are expected — net terms, early payment discounts, late penalties. Applied to invoices and billing statements.\n\n## Position in Ecosystem\n\nFinance & Billing zone. Provides payment configuration that [[invoice model generates formal payment requests]] and [[billing-statement model captures periodic billing summaries]] consume.\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[ecosystem map]]\n- [[object relations]]",
